      "span_text": "We used the mean of covariates method to produce adjusted survival curves for these final models.  We determined that the proportional hazard assumption was satisfied by examining plots of the log negative log of the within-group survivorship functions versus log-time, the Schoenfeld residuals, and Kaplan-Meier (observed) versus Cox (expected) survival curves."
